title: 'Boys and Girl - HOF Wide Receiver Terrell Owens Talks Cowboys Memories, Regrets, Controversy, Celebrations, Misconceptions
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - HOF Wide Receiver Terrell Owens Talks Cowboys Memories, Regrets, Controversy, Celebrations, Misconceptions
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby visit with Hall of Fame wide receiver Terrell Owens. T.O. talks about his time in Dallas, his career in general, and lots more in this wide-ranging discussion.

Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
